Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform up to three slashes forward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
During each attack's activation phase, pressing <IconMap:Icon_Special> will trigger [Ignition], causing this attack to deal additional <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color> and restore Adrenaline.

While [Ignited], press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform up to 4 slashes forward, dealing <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, if Komano Manato's HP is above 30%, consume 20% of max HP to trigger <color=#FFFFFF>[Core Passive]</color>.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> during a <color=#FFFFFF>Perfect Dodge</color> to activate:
Slash and punch enemies in front, dealing <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
Slash forward to deal <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color> to enemies;
If attacked by enemies during this skill, recover 20% of lost HP when slashing;
Take 40% less DMG during this skill;
Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.

Hold <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
Enter charging state, consuming up to 10% of max HP and recover 100 [Flame], HP can be consumed up to 30% of max HP;
Release [Special Attack] when releasing the button, if hit by enemy attacks during this skill, recover 20% of lost HP when performing the Slash;
Take 40% less DMG during this skill;
Anti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill.

While in [Ignited] state, with enough Adrenaline, press <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady_Rp> to activate:
Jump and perform a falling slash on enemies ahead, dealing massive <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, restore 33% of max HP;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When a <color=#FFFFFF>Chain Attack</color> is triggered, select the character to activate:
Throws their sword and charges at enemies to trigger an explosion, dealing massive <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When Decibel Rating is at <color=#FFFFFF>Maximum</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_UltimateReady> to activate:
Jump and unleash a falling slash at enemies ahead, followed by an explosion, dealing massive <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <IconMap:Icon_Switch> to activate:
Parries the enemy's attack, dealing massive Daze and <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, recover 75 [Flame] points;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>[Defensive Assist]</color> to activate:
Unleash multiple slashes against enemies in front, dealing <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>;
Repeatedly press to perform consecutive slashes, up to 7 additional times;
During consecutive slashes, if Komano Manato's HP is above 30%, consume 2% of max HP to trigger <color=#FFFFFF>[Core Passive]</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Desc:
Komano Manato gains additional Sheer Force based on his max HP, with each point of max HP increasing Sheer Force by 0.1;
All <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color> dealt by Komano Manato's skills becomes Sheer DMG that ignores enemy defense and uses Sheer Force as the DMG Multiplier;
When Komano Manato uses <color=#FFFFFF>[Special Attack: Hold]</color> or <color=#FFFFFF>[Defensive Assist]</color>, he accumulates <color=#FFFFFF>[Flame]</color>, up to 100 points; When <color=#FFFFFF>[Flame]</color> reaches 75 points, Komano Manato enters <color=#FFFFFF>[Ignited]</color> state until <color=#FFFFFF>[Flame]</color> is depleted;
While <color=#FFFFFF>[Ignited]</color>, Komano Manato's <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack]</color> is enhanced and he can use <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack]</color>;
When Komano Manato consumes max HP during consecutive slashes of <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Ignited]</color> or <color=#FFFFFF>[Assist Follow-Up]</color>, this attack's CRIT DMG increases by <color=#2BAD00>30%</color>, and Adrenaline recovery rate increases by 100%.
When [Ignited], Komano Manato's CRITCRIT Rate increases by {EXCEL:3}%.

